messages.title: 5 THINGS TO REMEMBER
messages.content:
1 You don't need your polling card to vote
2 Polls are open 7am -10pm
3 If you've got a postal vote, but haven't sent it back yet, you can take it to your polling station before 10pm
4 If you don't know where your polling station is or you need a lift to vote, call our campaign hotline on 01482 319 135
5 Place a X next to DIANA JOHNSON

mentions.tacticalSituation: USE ALL YOUR VOTES FOR LABOUR Place one X next to your Labour candidate for Hull North - Diana Johnson

leaflet.personalStatement: As your MP I will always stand up for Hull and speak out on issues that matter to you. Britain needs real change. It's time for a Labour Government.
